{"tid":253153,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"洗樓洗出TOT 做MPF保險客年薪過3百萬","createTime":"2017-05-22T07:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T03:49:23.000Z","uid":58319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad8d26d25dc4497031053e468c7d78a59b7eb57","tid":253153,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"「希望30歲之前可以買到車及樓，相信是大多年輕人的夢想。現在我車就買了，樓就仲睇緊。」咁後生就買車買樓，肯定靠父幹啦？No！No！No！其實全部都是他的血汗錢。今年28歲的Alvin，修讀旅遊及酒店管理高級文憑，他在10年畢業後加入過銀行業，但其後因收入不似預期轉而投身保險業。 <br />\n<br />\nAlvin說：「初入行時，身邊的朋友都未畢業，他們的經濟能力不好，因為大家都初起步，所以當時冇客見，愈冇客見我個心態就愈差。當時的財政都非常差，戶口是冇錢，可能只有八十多元，根本不能提出來。回到家都要面對父母，壓力好大，於是便做些兼職，例如餐廳，甚至走水貨，至少我可以畀到家用開到飯。」 <br />\n<br />\n心灰意冷的Alvin，在朋友介紹下認識到現時的上司Corey及Yedda，教他找MPF(強積金)的公司客增加業績，於是他便轉去永明金融，加入Corey團隊。Alvin說：「我目標一日要見3個客，但未必日日都達標，我便會去洗樓或coldcall，一定要想盡辦法填滿日程。夏天會比較辛苦，?住恤衫，汗流浹背，好似游完水。男仔洗樓冇咁?數，女生的話，客人普遍憐香惜玉，相反男仔，客人會趕你走、用粗口鬧你。不過都無所謂，見唔成咪下一個客人。」 <br />\n<br />\nAlvin從此展開他的洗樓生涯，到各區的工廈洗樓找公司MPF客，做了1個月，他已經成功簽了幾間公司的MPF，由於不是每間公司的MPF都有agent跟進，所以Alvin用這個位切入向公司推銷，他會提供匯報升跌數據，教員工如何管理自己的帳目，有疑問時亦可隨時找他。 <br />\n<br />\n做了不久Alvin已略有成績，第一年的收入已有36萬，16年，Alvin升為營業經理，佣金更超過3百萬，成為TOT的一員。「幸運地獲得Top Of The Table(TOT)，頂尖會員的一個資格。上年簽了十多間公司，都是商會的老闆，因為認識他們久了便很信任我，所以他們公司的強積金、保險，甚至個人保險都是由我負責。」 <br />\n<br />\nAlvin上司Corey表示：「我的團隊強項是coldcall，有大量客源給Alvin，在有客源的情況下，他便可以有好的表現。Alvin是一個願意學習的人，好快已經從舊同事身上汲取技巧，他成功的時間比其他同事快。」 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E9%9D%92%E9%9B%B2%E8%B7%AF/article/20170519/2_512298_0/-%E9%9D%92%E9%9B%B2%E8%B7%AF-%E6%B4%97%E6%A8%93%E6%B4%97%E5%87%BATOT-%E5%81%9AMPF%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%AE%A2%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA%E9%81%8E3%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%259B%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF%2Farticle%2F20170519%2F2_512298_0%2F-%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%259B%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%2587%25BATOT-%25E5%2581%259AMPF%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA%25E9%2581%258E3%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC&d=WsZpLEGudxUbfaIdpI%2FiYiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=aaa6c3a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%259B%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF%2Farticle%2F20170519%2F2_512298_0%2F-%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%259B%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%2587%25BATOT-%25E5%2581%259AMPF%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA%25E9%2581%258E3%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC&h=f7e7f49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E9%9D%92%E9%9B%B2%E8%B7%AF/article/20170519/2_512298_0/-%E9%9D%92%E9%9B%B2%E8%B7%AF-%E6%B4%97%E6%A8%93%E6%B4%97%E5%87%BATOT-%E5%81%9AMPF%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E5%AE%A2%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA%E9%81%8E3%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"093f6ebde357f61776c18b4ecbfa9907305eacd3","tid":253153,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"好勁呀"},{"pid":"d8861cd18700f371a48d4fd4b39e05d9ca3175fc","tid":253153,"uid":91283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"我的團隊強項是coldcall，有大量客源給Alvin<br />\n<br />\n有大量客源仲洗cold call?"},{"pid":"73333c2991fce30c79739295c152baa955c4beb8","tid":253153,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"真係幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696af13c0bb57766d45e0a865619ccd3fe38df6e","tid":253153,"uid":91283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n膳文黎姐"},{"pid":"f6061ce8ab641f7ad7c4797fc7ebfafd67c43bed","tid":253153,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"一係Uncle 開公司<br />\n一係老豆都係佢上司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe238e0b3a146d79669dcea554441839bc85c6","tid":253153,"uid":37798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"睇完篇文之後好想做MPF呀 好想加入TOT呀 點申請架?"},{"pid":"d891e9534a47fef979210a3aa091b7eca1c2dd73","tid":253153,"uid":58319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完篇文之後好想做MPF呀 好想加入TOT呀 點申請架?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d9cd3e2bbaa9deb9eef95d169b2b776f988cb1","tid":253153,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:42:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以有啲新意?"},{"pid":"33c79b172a4f44b6d9ff4f74369fe1772fc60d88","tid":253153,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c7b88743ad69fb7206ebe3fcfc40087d6f2db61","tid":253153,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">於是他便轉去永明金融，加入Corey團隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點解要加入團隊，有無口號？</span></span>"},{"pid":"d24b8c8e816b802edbc8e0dbfda5485a73cf73e9","tid":253153,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"同事coldcall佢接客<br />\n做推銷最辛苦就係搵客<br />\n客就下層搵"}]}